
Inculta Creperum Quest:

Physical challenge: 6 or 7
Mental challenge: 3 or 4

Search the dark desert and assemble the wand to
free the Soul of the Desert Sand from its prison.

From Zeus' castle: n, in, touch orb, say desert
wander around the area 'search'ing until you find the 3 pieces of the wand.
(you must kill the monsters in a room before you can search)
assemble pieces into full wand
kill the brute lord, in ec9 (west most room)
get the cloak and type 'free soul'


Note
(to find where the pieces are, type:
exec "/players/zeus/desert/OBJ/desert_daemon.c"->show_what_rooms_have_wand_pieces(this_player());

